title: Salvador Dali 2023 Wall Calendar
description:
Salvador Dali is one of the most well known surrealist artists to ever live. Using symbolism, imagination and memories to create incredible works of art. Persistence of Time and Galatea of the Spheres are represented in this fascinating 12 month calendar.

This 12" x 12" calendar includes major international holidays, lunar phases, and zodiac signs.
  • Dimensions: 11.75 x 11.75 in.
  • Materials: Shrink-wrapped with a sturdy cardboard insert.
  • Features 7 languages: Italian, English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Japanese.
